{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm a neuroscientist, a professor at the University of California."},{"time":3000,"text":"And over the past 35 years,"},{"time":6000,"text":"I've studied behavior"},{"time":8000,"text":"on the basis of everything from genes"},{"time":11000,"text":"through neurotransmitters, dopamine, things like that,"},{"time":13000,"text":"all the way through circuit analysis."},{"time":15000,"text":"So that's what I normally do."},{"time":17000,"text":"But then, for some reason,"},{"time":19000,"text":"I got into something else, just recently."},{"time":21000,"text":"And it all grew out of one of my colleagues asking me"},{"time":24000,"text":"to analyze a bunch of brains"},{"time":26000,"text":"of psychopathic killers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28000,"text":"And so this would be the typical talk I would give."},{"time":31000,"text":"And the question is, \"How do you end up with a psychopathic killer?\""},{"time":34000,"text":"What I mean by psychopathic killer"},{"time":36000,"text":"are these people, these types of people."},{"time":38000,"text":"And so some of the brains that I've studied"},{"time":40000,"text":"are people you know about."},{"time":42000,"text":"When I get the brains I don't know what I'm looking at."},{"time":44000,"text":"It's blind experiments. They also gave me normal people and everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"So I've looked at about 70 of these."},{"time":48000,"text":"And what came up was a number of pieces of data."},{"time":51000,"text":"So we look at these sorts of things theoretically,"},{"time":54000,"text":"on the basis of genetics,"},{"time":56000,"text":"and brain damage, and interaction with environment,"},{"time":59000,"text":"and exactly how that machine works."},{"time":61000,"text":"So we're interested in exactly where in the brain,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and what's the most important part of the brain."},{"time":65000,"text":"So we've been looking at this:"},{"time":68000,"text":"the interaction of genes,"},{"time":70000,"text":"what's called epigenetic effects,"},{"time":72000,"text":"brain damage, and environment,"},{"time":74000,"text":"and how these are tied together."},{"time":76000,"text":"And how you end up with a psychopath, and a killer,"},{"time":78000,"text":"depends on exactly when the damage occurs."},{"time":81000,"text":"It's really a very precisely timed thing."},{"time":84000,"text":"You get different kinds of psychopaths."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"So we're going along with this. And here's, just to give you the pattern."},{"time":89000,"text":"The pattern is that those people, every one of them I looked at,"},{"time":92000,"text":"who was a murderer, and was a serial killer,"},{"time":95000,"text":"had damage to their orbital cortex,"},{"time":97000,"text":"which is right above the eyes, the orbits,"},{"time":99000,"text":"and also the interior part of the temporal lobe."},{"time":101000,"text":"So there is the pattern that every one of them had,"},{"time":103000,"text":"but they all were a little different too."},{"time":105000,"text":"They had other sorts of brain damage."},{"time":107000,"text":"A key thing is that"},{"time":109000,"text":"the major violence genes,"},{"time":112000,"text":"it's called the MAO-A gene."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"And there is a variant of this gene that is in the normal population."},{"time":119000,"text":"Some of you have this. And it's sex-linked."},{"time":122000,"text":"It's on the X chromosome. And so in this way"},{"time":124000,"text":"you can only get it from your mother."},{"time":127000,"text":"And in fact this is probably why mostly men, boys,"},{"time":131000,"text":"are psychopathic killers,"},{"time":133000,"text":"or are very aggressive."},{"time":135000,"text":"Because a daughter can get one X from the father,"},{"time":138000,"text":"one X from the mother, it's kind of diluted out."},{"time":140000,"text":"But for a son, he can only get"},{"time":142000,"text":"the X chromosome from his mother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":144000,"text":"So this is how it's passed from mother to son."},{"time":147000,"text":"And it has to do with too much brain serotonin during development,"},{"time":151000,"text":"which is kind of interesting because serotonin"},{"time":153000,"text":"is supposed to make you calm and relaxed."},{"time":156000,"text":"But if you have this gene, in utero"},{"time":159000,"text":"your brain is bathed in this,"},{"time":161000,"text":"so your whole brain becomes insensitive to serotonin,"},{"time":163000,"text":"so it doesn't work later on in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"And I'd given this one talk in Israel,"},{"time":169000,"text":"just this past year."},{"time":171000,"text":"And it does have some consequences."},{"time":173000,"text":"Theoretically what this means"},{"time":175000,"text":"is that in order to express this gene,"},{"time":178000,"text":"in a violent way,"},{"time":180000,"text":"very early on, before puberty,"},{"time":182000,"text":"you have to be involved in something that is really traumatic --"},{"time":185000,"text":"not a little stress, not being spanked or something,"},{"time":187000,"text":"but really seeing violence,"},{"time":189000,"text":"or being involved in it, in 3D."},{"time":191000,"text":"Right? That's how the mirror neuron system works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"And so, if you have that gene,"},{"time":196000,"text":"and you see a lot of violence"},{"time":199000,"text":"in a certain situation,"},{"time":201000,"text":"this is the recipe for disaster, absolute disaster."},{"time":204000,"text":"And what I think might happen in these areas of the world,"},{"time":207000,"text":"where we have constant violence,"},{"time":210000,"text":"you end up having generations of kids"},{"time":213000,"text":"that are seeing all this violence."},{"time":215000,"text":"And if I was a young girl, somewhere in a violent area,"},{"time":218000,"text":"you know, a 14 year old, and I want to find a mate,"},{"time":220000,"text":"I'd find some tough guy, right, to protect me."},{"time":223000,"text":"Well what the problem is this tends to concentrate these genes."},{"time":227000,"text":"And now the boys and the girls get them."},{"time":229000,"text":"So I think after several generations,"},{"time":231000,"text":"and here is the idea, we really have a tinderbox."}]},{"cues":[{"time":234000,"text":"So that was the idea."},{"time":236000,"text":"But then my mother said to me, \"I hear you've been going around talking"},{"time":238000,"text":"about psychopathic killers."},{"time":241000,"text":"And you're talking as if you come from a normal family.\""},{"time":244000,"text":"I said, \"What the hell are you talking about?\""},{"time":246000,"text":"She then told me about our own family tree."},{"time":249000,"text":"Now she blamed this on my father's side, of course."},{"time":251000,"text":"This was one of these cases, because she has no violence in her background,"},{"time":255000,"text":"but my father did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257000,"text":"Well she said, \"There is good news and bad news."},{"time":259000,"text":"One of your cousins is Ezra Cornell, founder of Cornell university."},{"time":262000,"text":"But the bad news is that your cousin is also Lizzie Borden."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265000,"text":"Now I said, \"Okay, so what? We have Lizzie.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":272000,"text":"She goes, \"No it gets worse, read this book.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":274000,"text":"And here is this \"Killed Strangely,\" and it's this historical book."},{"time":276000,"text":"And the first murder"},{"time":278000,"text":"of a mother by a son"},{"time":280000,"text":"was my great-great-great-great-great-great-grandfather."},{"time":283000,"text":"Okay, so that's the first case of matricide."},{"time":286000,"text":"And that book is very interesting. Because it's about witch trials,"},{"time":289000,"text":"and how people thought back then."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291000,"text":"But it doesn't stop there."},{"time":293000,"text":"There were seven more men, on my father's side,"},{"time":296000,"text":"starting then, Cornells, that were all murderers."},{"time":300000,"text":"Okay, now this gives one a little pause."},{"time":303000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":305000,"text":"Because my father himself,"},{"time":307000,"text":"and my three uncles, in World War II,"},{"time":309000,"text":"were all conscientious objectors, all pussycats."},{"time":312000,"text":"But every once in a while, like Lizzie Borden, like three times a century,"},{"time":314000,"text":"and we're kind of due."},{"time":316000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319000,"text":"So the moral of the story is:"},{"time":321000,"text":"people in glass houses shouldn't throw stones."},{"time":323000,"text":"But more likely is this."},{"time":326000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":330000,"text":"And we had to take action. Now our kids found out about it."},{"time":333000,"text":"And they all seemed to be OK."},{"time":335000,"text":"But our grandkids are going to be kind of concerned here."},{"time":338000,"text":"So what we've done is I've started to do PET scans"},{"time":341000,"text":"of everybody in the family."},{"time":343000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":344000,"text":"We started to do PET scans, EEGs and genetic analysis"},{"time":347000,"text":"to see where the bad news is."},{"time":349000,"text":"Now the only person -- it turns out"},{"time":351000,"text":"one son and one daughter, siblings,"},{"time":354000,"text":"didn't get along and their patterns are exactly the same."},{"time":356000,"text":"They have the same brain, and the same EEG."},{"time":359000,"text":"And now they are close as can be."},{"time":362000,"text":"But there's gonna be bad news somewhere."},{"time":364000,"text":"And we don't know where it's going to pop up."},{"time":366000,"text":"So that's my talk."},{"time":368000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]}]}